&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours: &lt;/strong&gt;37.5&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;The Willow Group, Gosport, Hampshire&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Southern Health Foundation Trust has an exciting opportunity for an experienced Practice Nurse to join The Willow Group, a forward thinking and innovative GP group providing primary care services for 35,000 patients over 4 local sites in Gosport.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, caring and motivated professional with excellent clinical, organisational &amp; communication skills, who has the ability to work autonomously.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will be an experienced nurse who, acting within their professional boundaries, will support our on-going initiatives:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GP Same Day Access Service &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The aim of the service is to make it easier for people to receive a same day consultation with the relevant healthcare professional be that a GP, Nurse, Physiotherapist or Mental Health Practitioner. By bringing patients who require same day care into one area, we can make better use of clinical resources and expertise.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Acute Home Visiting Service&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Effective and consistent clinical triage to make sure all patients requesting home visits receive the right level of response according to need i.e. GP, ANP, Community Nurse, Paramedic etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Long Term Conditions Hub&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Our Long Term Conditions Hub for Diabetes, COPD, Asthma and CHD, which along with our Specialist Practice Nurses, also include Community and Hospital sepecialists to work together to provide an enhanced service for our patients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Happy to talk flexible working&lt;/strong&gt;-&lt;strong&gt; all requests for flexible and part time working will be considered.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
